---
// AiJourney.astro
---

<section class="ai-journey" id="ai-journey">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">The AI Journey</h2>
    
    <div class="glass-panel journey-content animate-slide-up delay-200">
      <div class="narrative">
        <p class="intro">
          My relationship with AI started with deep skepticism. Like many seasoned engineers, I was critical of the noise. But that very skepticism led me to dive deep, and the deeper I went, the more it transformed my workflow.
        </p>
        
        <div class="stack-showcase">
          <div class="stack-item">
            <span class="icon">🌌</span>
            <h4>Antigravity</h4>
            <p>Gemini 3.5</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-item">
            <span class="icon">⚡</span>
            <h4>Codex</h4>
            <p>OpenAI 5.5</p>
          </div>
          <div class="stack-item">
            <span class="icon">🧠</span>
            <h4>ClaudeCode</h4>
            <p>Opus 4.7</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="outro">
          Today, I don't just use cloud-based AI. I am heavily invested in new hardware to master self-hosted, local AI models. Running <strong>Ollama</strong> and <strong>Stable Diffusion</strong> on local rigs has become my latest frontier—giving me the privacy, speed, and deep understanding of LLM architecture necessary for next-generation engineering.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="visual-hardware">
        <div class="chip">
          <div class="chip-inner">AI Core</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ai-journey {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
  }

  .journey-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    .journey-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }

  .intro, .outro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .intro {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .outro {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary-accent);
    padding-left: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .outro strong {
    color: var(--secondary-accent);
  }

  .stack-showcase {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
  }

  .stack-item {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 120px;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast), border-color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .stack-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--primary-accent);
  }

  .stack-item .icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }

  .stack-item h4 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .stack-item p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .visual-hardware {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .chip {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a2f3a 0%, #16191f 100%);
    border-radius: 20px;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 
      0 0 0 2px #3a4150,
      0 0 30px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    animation: breathing-glow 4s infinite alternate;
  }

  .chip::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px; left: 20px; right: 20px; bottom: -10px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 10px, #3a4150 10px, #3a4150 15px);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .chip::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -10px; top: 20px; bottom: 20px; right: -10px;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 10px, #3a4150 10px, #3a4150 15px);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .chip-inner {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background: #0b0d10;
    border: 1px solid var(--primary-accent);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--primary-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.2);
  }

  @keyframes breathing-glow {
    0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px #3a4150, 0 0 20px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.05); }
    100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px #3a4150, 0 0 40px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.3); }
  }
</style>
